#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.filter.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.filter"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:1 of
msgid ""
"Subset the dataframe rows or columns according to the specified index "
"labels."
msgstr "根据指定的索引标签对 DataFrame 的行或列进行子集筛选。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:3 of
msgid ""
"Note that this routine does not filter a dataframe on its contents. The "
"filter is applied to the labels of the index."
msgstr "请注意，此例程不会根据 DataFrame 的内容进行筛选。筛选是应用于索引标签的。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:6 of
msgid "Keep labels from axis which are in items."
msgstr "保留轴上在 items 中的标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:8 of
msgid "Keep labels from axis for which \"like in label == True\"."
msgstr "保留轴上满足 \"like in label == True\" 的标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:10 of
msgid "Keep labels from axis for which re.search(regex, label) == True."
msgstr "保留轴上满足 re.search(regex, label) == True 的标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:12 of
msgid ""
"The axis to filter on, expressed either as an index (int) or axis name "
"(str). By default this is the info axis, 'columns' for DataFrame. For "
"`Series` this parameter is unused and defaults to `None`."
msgstr ""
"要筛选的轴，可以表示为索引（int）或轴名称（str）。默认为信息轴，对于 "
"DataFrame 是 'columns'。对于 `Series` 此参数未使用，默认为 `None`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.loc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:22 of
msgid "Access a group of rows and columns by label(s) or a boolean array."
msgstr "通过标签或布尔数组访问一组行和列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:25 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:26 of
msgid ""
"The ``items``, ``like``, and ``regex`` parameters are enforced to be "
"mutually exclusive."
msgstr "``items``、``like`` 和 ``regex`` 参数被强制互斥。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:29 of
msgid "``axis`` defaults to the info axis that is used when indexing with ``[]``."
msgstr "``axis`` 默认为使用 ``[]`` 索引时的信息轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.filter.filter_dataframe:33 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

